'''Blanche Bilongo''' (yavutse ku ya 26 Mutarama 1974) ni umukinnyi wa filime, umwanditsi wa filimi  wo muri [[Kameruni]].

== Ubuzima bwa Biografiya ==
Bilongo akomoka muri [[Kameruni|Cameroni]] hagati  <ref>https://www.237online.com/wob1ihus/</ref> Yize muri kaminuza ya Johnson muri Yaoundé akora ballet. Mu 1987, yatangiye kwitabira imyitozo yitsinda ryamakinamico ya Les Pagayeurs ya André Bang kandi yafashe mu mutwe imirongo yabigizemo uruhare. Umunsi umwe, ubwo umukinnyi wa mbere utari uhari, Bilongo yamusimbuye kandi imikorere ye yemeje abantu bose. Bilongo yaje kwinjira muri iryo tsinda. <ref name="atanga">https://fr.allafrica.com/stories/200504150745.html</ref>

Bilongo yatangiye gukina filime mu 2000, i ''Tiga, L'Héritage'' .  Muri 2005, Bilongo yakinnye nka Sabine kuri opera yisabune ''N'taphil'' .  Muri 2007, yakinnye Pam muri firime ya ''Les Blessures Inguérissables ya'' Hélène Patricia Ebah . Imico ye ivuga kubura umugabo we akamenya ko ubuzima bwe bwabaye ibinyoma. <ref>http://www.cameroon-info.net/article/yaounde-un-week-end-de-danse-et-de-comedie-106911.html</ref> Yabaye umwanditsi wa televiziyo CRTV mu 2009. <ref name="mere">http://www.crtv.cm/2019/02/musique-blanche-bilongo-rend-hommage-a-sa-mere/</ref>

Muri Gicurasi 2015, Bilongo yahawe izina rya Knight of the Order of Valor, nyuma y’icyifuzo cya Minisitiri w’ubuhanzi n’umuco Narcisse Mouelle Kombi. <ref>http://www.cinecamer.info/index.php/fr/les-gens/45-blanche-bilongo-la-nation-reconnaissante</ref> Muri 2019, Bilongo yasohoye indirimbo ye ya mbere, "Le temps de Dieu". Yaririmbwe mu rurimi rwa Beti kandi yeguriwe nyina wapfuye.  Muri 2020, yakinnye nka Marie Young muri comedi y'urukundo ''Coup de Foudre à Yaoundé'' . <ref>{{Template:Cite web}}</ref>

